<view class="sanctuary-page contact-page">
  <view class="topbar">
    <view class="avatar-shell"><view class="avatar-shell__core">V</view></view>
    <view class="topbar-spacer"></view>
    <view class="topbar-action" bindtap="goRedeem">券</view>
  </view>

  <view class="container topbar-offset contact-page__content">
    <view class="contact-hero">
      <view class="hero-display">课程咨询<br />与开通</view>
      <view class="body-copy">先确认学习方向和课程权益，再通过兑换码开通完整训练路径。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="surface-card contact-card">
      <view class="contact-card__leaf"></view>
      <view class="warm-badge">CONSULT</view>
      <view class="contact-card__title">咨询前可先说明学习方向</view>
      <view class="section-subtitle">例如：想练北越标准音，或想练南越日常交流发音。这样更容易获得合适的购买建议。</view>
      <button class="btn-primary mt-32" bindtap="copyConsult">复制咨询说明</button>
      <button class="btn-secondary mt-16" bindtap="copyPurchaseFlow">复制开通流程</button>
    </view>

    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">常见问题</view>
      <view class="section-link">FAQ</view>
    </view>
    <view class="contact-faq">
      <view class="surface-wrap contact-faq__item">
        <view class="contact-faq__mark">01</view>
        <view>
          <view class="contact-faq__title">课程开通后多久有效？</view>
          <view class="contact-faq__copy">当前版本按长期使用权益处理，后续内容更新会继续保留学习记录。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="surface-wrap contact-faq__item">
        <view class="contact-faq__mark">02</view>
        <view>
          <view class="contact-faq__title">北越和南越都能学习吗？</view>
          <view class="contact-faq__copy">完整课程会同时解锁两套路径，学习进度分开保存。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="surface-wrap contact-faq__item">
        <view class="contact-faq__mark">03</view>
        <view>
          <view class="contact-faq__title">购买后如何开通？</view>
          <view class="contact-faq__copy">拿到兑换码后，回到小程序「个人」页面输入即可开通。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
